Package org.nerd4j.csv.field

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CSVFieldConverter<S,T>
    Represents a converter able to convert the CSV field in String into is object oriented representation and vice versa.
    CSVFieldValidator<V>
    Represents a class able to check a condition over the given CSV field.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CSVField<S,T>
    This class performs the process needed to manipulate a CSV field from its String form to its Object representation and vice versa.
    CSVFieldMetadata<S,T>
    Represents the meta-data that describes how to handle a single field in the CSV process.
    CSVFieldProcessContext
    Represents the execution context of the during the process of validating and converting fields.
    CSVFieldProcessor<S,T>
    This class performs the process needed to manipulate a CSV field from its String form to its Object representation and vice versa.
